
{help f_invchi2:English Version}
{hline}
{* *! version 1.1.1  02mar2015}{...}
    {cmd:invchi2(}{it:df}{cmd:,}{it:p}{cmd:)}
{p2colset 8 22 22 2}{...}
{p2col: 描述：} {cmd:chi2()} 的逆：如果
	{cmd:chi2(}{it:df}{cmd:,}x{cmd:)} = {it:p}，那么
	{cmd:invchi2(}{it:df}{cmd:,}{it:p}{cmd:)} = {it:x}{p_end}
{p2col: 域 {it:df}:} 2e-10 到 2e+17（可能是非整数）{p_end}
{p2col: 域 {it:p}:} 0 到 1{p_end}
{p2col: 范围：} 0 到 8e+307{p_end}
{p2colreset}{...}